    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n th\xEDch m\xF9i ng\u1ECDt \u1EA5m ki\u1EC3u gourmand hay vanilla th\xEC Profumo kh\xF4ng h\u1EE3p \u2014 \u0111\xE2y ho\xE0n to\xE0n l\xE0 h\u01B0\u1EDBng aquatic-aromatic. Ai mu\u1ED1n m\xF9i c\u1EF1c n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt, g\xE2y \u1EA5n t\u01B0\u1EE3ng m\u1EA1nh c\u0169ng s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y Profumo h\u01A1i an to\xE0n v\xEC n\xF3 thi\xEAn v\u1EC1 s\u1EF1 c\xE2n b\u1EB1ng h\u01A1n l\xE0 ph\xF4 tr\u01B0\u01A1ng. Ngo\xE0i ra, n\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n \u0111\xE3 c\xF3 Acqua di Gi\xF2 Parfum (b\u1EA3n m\u1EDBi h\u01A1n 2022) th\xEC 2 chai kh\xE1 g\u1EA7n nhau, c\xE2n nh\u1EAFc tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi mua th\xEAm.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Profumo thu\u1ED9c ph\xE2n kh\xFAc designer cao c\u1EA5p \u2014 gi\xE1 t\u01B0\u01A1ng \u0111\u01B0\u01A1ng Bleu de Chanel EDP hay Dior Sauvage EDP. So v\u1EDBi b\u1EA3n g\u1ED1c Acqua di Gi\xF2 EDT, Profumo tr\u01B0\u1EDFng th\xE0nh h\u01A1n, s\xE2u h\u01A1n v\xE0 b\xE1m l\xE2u h\u01A1n \u0111\xE1ng k\u1EC3. So v\u1EDBi Bleu de Chanel EDP, Profumo thi\xEAn bi\u1EC3n h\u01A1n v\xE0 \xEDt g\u1ED7 h\u01A1n. Hi\u1EC7u n\u0103ng r\u1EA5t t\u1ED1t cho ph\xE2n kh\xFAc: 7-8 gi\u1EDD l\u01B0u h\u01B0\u01A1ng, t\u1ECFa m\u1EA1nh 3-4 gi\u1EDD \u0111\u1EA7u. Chai fullbox d\xF9ng r\u1EA5t l\xE2u v\xEC ch\u1EC9 c\u1EA7n 2-3 nh\xE1t. N\xEAn mua chi\u1EBFt 10ml th\u1EED tr\u01B0\u1EDBc.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

D\xF9ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c quanh n\u0103m \u2014 \u0111i l\xE0m, \u0111i ch\u01A1i, du l\u1ECBch, h\u1EB9n h\xF2 nh\u1EB9. \u0110\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t v\xE0o m\xF9a xu\xE2n v\xE0 h\xE8 khi tr\u1EDDi \u1EA5m (25-32\xB0C), nh\u01B0ng m\xF9a thu c\u0169ng r\u1EA5t \u1ED5n. X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t: 1 sau g\xE1y, 1 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc ng\u1EF1c, 1 c\u1ED5 tay. \u1EDE S\xE0i G\xF2n d\xF9ng ban ng\xE0y r\u1EA5t tho\u1EA3i m\xE1i v\xEC bi\u1EC3n + th\u1EA3o m\u1ED9c kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD ng\u1ECDp. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 ki\u1EC3u chai an to\xE0n cho m\u1ECDi ho\xE0n c\u1EA3nh \u2014 hi\u1EBFm khi n\xE0o x\u1ECBt Profumo m\xE0 sai.`,
