    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n ngh\u0129 vani = ng\u1ECDt ng\xE0o \u1EA5m \xE1p d\u1EC5 th\u01B0\u01A1ng th\xEC Ang\xE9lique Noire s\u1EBD ph\xE1 v\u1EE1 \u0111\u1ECBnh ki\u1EBFn \u0111\xF3. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 "vani xanh" \u2014 b\u1EA1ch ch\u1EC9 (angelica) t\u1EA1o ra l\u1EDBp \u0111\u1EAFng th\u1EA3o m\u1ED9c ph\u1EE7 l\xEAn vani, gi\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0 cocktail gin & tonic thay v\xEC milkshake. Ai th\xEDch gourmand ng\u1ECDt r\xF5 r\xE0ng s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y n\xF3 l\u1EA1 v\xE0 kh\xF3 hi\u1EC3u. Gi\xE1 d\xF2ng L'Art et la Mati\xE8re c\u1EE7a Guerlain c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng friendly.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

D\xF2ng L'Art et la Mati\xE8re \u2014 exclusive line cao nh\u1EA5t Guerlain. Daniela Andrier (perfumer c\u1EE7a Prada Infusion d'Iris) t\u1EA1o ra concept "v\u0169 \u0111\u1EA1o c\u1EE7a \u0111\u1ED1i l\u1EADp": t\u01B0\u01A1i vs \u1EA5m, \u0111\u1EAFng vs ng\u1ECDt, xanh vs vani. So v\u1EDBi Tom Ford Tobacco Vanille \u2014 c\xF9ng vani cao c\u1EA5p \u2014 th\xEC Ang\xE9lique Noire s\u1EA1ch h\u01A1n r\u1EA5t nhi\u1EC1u, kh\xF4ng ng\u1ECDt, kh\xF4ng thu\u1ED1c l\xE1. So v\u1EDBi MFK Grand Soir \u2014 c\xF9ng vani amber niche \u2014 th\xEC Ang\xE9lique Noire xanh h\u01A1n, nh\u1EB9 h\u01A1n. B\xE1m 8-10 gi\u1EDD.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

\u0110i gallery, \u0103n t\u1ED1i sang, s\u1EF1 ki\u1EC7n ngh\u1EC7 thu\u1EADt, ho\u1EB7c khi n\xE0o mu\u1ED1n m\xF9i h\u01B0\u01A1ng l\xE0 t\xE1c ph\u1EA9m ch\u1EE9 kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i ph\u1EE5 ki\u1EC7n. X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t: c\u1ED5 v\xE0 c\u1ED5 tay. D\xF9ng quanh n\u0103m \u2014 b\u1EA1ch ch\u1EC9 gi\u1EEF t\u01B0\u01A1i m\xF9a h\xE8, vani gi\u1EEF \u1EA5m m\xF9a \u0111\xF4ng. Chai d\xE0nh cho ng\u01B0\u1EDDi hi\u1EC3u n\u01B0\u1EDBc hoa.`,
