    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n th\xEDch m\xF9i ng\u1ECDt \u0111\u1EADm sexy ki\u1EC3u Good Girl hay Black Opium th\xEC Armani S\xEC s\u1EBD qu\xE1 nh\u1EB9 v\xE0 qu\xE1 l\u1ECBch s\u1EF1 cho gu \u0111\xF3. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 m\xF9i thanh l\u1ECBch, c\xE2n b\u1EB1ng \u2014 kh\xF4ng qu\xE1 ng\u1ECDt, kh\xF4ng qu\xE1 n\u1ED5i. Ai th\xEDch m\xF9i tr\u1EBB trung vui v\u1EBB ki\u1EC3u tr\xE1i c\xE2y ng\u1ECDt c\u0169ng s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y S\xEC h\u01A1i mature. Ngo\xE0i ra, n\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n mu\u1ED1n m\xF9i beast mode t\u1ECFa xa th\xEC S\xEC EDP kh\xF4ng thu\u1ED9c nh\xF3m \u0111\xF3.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Armani S\xEC thu\u1ED9c ph\xE2n kh\xFAc designer t\u1EA7m trung \u2014 r\u1EBB h\u01A1n Coco Mademoiselle v\xE0 Miss Dior EDP. So v\u1EDBi Coco Mademoiselle, S\xEC \xEDt citrus h\u01A1n nh\u01B0ng ng\u1ECDt tr\xE1i c\xE2y h\u01A1n \u1EDF \u0111\u1EA7u. So v\u1EDBi Miss Dior EDP, S\xEC \xEDt hoa h\u1ED3ng h\u01A1n nh\u01B0ng c\xF3 cassis r\u1EA5t \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng. Hi\u1EC7u n\u0103ng kh\xE1: b\xE1m 6-7 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa v\u1EEBa. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 ki\u1EC3u chai safe \u2014 h\u1EA7u nh\u01B0 kh\xF4ng ai gh\xE9t S\xEC. N\xEAn mua chi\u1EBFt 10ml th\u1EED tr\u01B0\u1EDBc.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

D\xF9ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c quanh n\u0103m \u2014 \u0111i l\xE0m, g\u1EB7p kh\xE1ch, \u0111i \u0103n t\u1ED1i nh\u1EB9. X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t: c\u1ED5, c\u1ED5 tay, sau tai. \u0110\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t v\xE0o m\xF9a xu\xE2n thu. \u1EDE S\xE0i G\xF2n d\xF9ng tho\u1EA3i m\xE1i v\xEC kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD ng\u1ECDp. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 ki\u1EC3u chai signature l\xFD t\u01B0\u1EDFng cho ph\u1EE5 n\u1EEF \u0111i l\xE0m \u2014 thanh l\u1ECBch, chuy\xEAn nghi\u1EC7p v\xE0 d\u1EC5 ch\u1ECBu.`,
