    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n th\xEDch c\u1EA3m gi\xE1c t\u01B0\u01A1i s\xE1ng, b\xF9ng n\u1ED5 c\u1EE7a Bleu de Chanel EDT hay EDP th\xEC b\u1EA3n Parfum s\u1EBD h\u01A1i k\xEDn v\xE0 thi\u1EBFu n\u0103ng l\u01B0\u1EE3ng so v\u1EDBi k\u1EF3 v\u1ECDng. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 b\u1EA3n tr\u01B0\u1EDFng th\xE0nh nh\u1EA5t \u2014 \xEDt citrus h\u01A1n, \xEDt "blue" h\u01A1n. Ai d\u01B0\u1EDBi 25 tu\u1ED5i th\xEDch m\xF9i tr\u1EBB trung, dynamic c\u0169ng s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y Parfum h\u01A1i gi\xE0 so v\u1EDBi m\xECnh. Ngo\xE0i ra, hi\u1EC7u n\u0103ng t\u1ECFa v\u1EEBa ph\u1EA3i \u2014 kh\xF4ng thu\u1ED9c nh\xF3m beast mode.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Bleu Parfum \u0111\u1EAFt h\u01A1n b\u1EA3n EDP kho\u1EA3ng 15-20% nh\u01B0ng cho c\u1EA3m gi\xE1c ho\xE0n thi\u1EC7n v\xE0 sang h\u01A1n r\xF5. So v\u1EDBi Bleu EDP, Parfum m\u01B0\u1EE3t h\u01A1n, \u1EA5m h\u01A1n v\xE0 c\xF3 chi\u1EC1u s\xE2u h\u01A1n nh\u01B0ng \xEDt t\u01B0\u01A1i h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi Dior Sauvage Elixir c\xF9ng ph\xE2n kh\xFAc "b\u1EA3n cao nh\u1EA5t", Bleu Parfum thanh l\u1ECBch h\u01A1n v\xE0 \xEDt n\u1EB7ng h\u01A1n. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 chai h\u1EE3p l\xE0m signature l\xE2u d\xE0i v\xEC r\u1EA5t \xEDt khi n\xE0o sai. N\xEAn mua chi\u1EBFt 10ml th\u1EED tr\u01B0\u1EDBc n\u1EBFu \u0111ang ph\xE2n v\xE2n gi\u1EEFa EDP v\xE0 Parfum.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

D\xF9ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c quanh n\u0103m nh\u01B0ng \u0111\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t m\xF9a thu \u0111\xF4ng v\xE0 tr\u1EDDi m\xE1t. H\u1EE3p \u0111i l\xE0m, g\u1EB7p kh\xE1ch, d\u1EF1 ti\u1EC7c ho\u1EB7c b\u1EA5t k\u1EF3 d\u1ECBp n\xE0o c\u1EA7n h\xECnh \u1EA3nh l\u1ECBch thi\u1EC7p. X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t: 1 sau g\xE1y, 1 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc ng\u1EF1c, 1 c\u1ED5 tay. \u1EDE S\xE0i G\xF2n d\xF9ng ban ng\xE0y trong ph\xF2ng m\xE1y l\u1EA1nh r\u1EA5t \u0111\u1EB9p. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 ki\u1EC3u m\xF9i an to\xE0n cao \u2014 g\u1EA7n nh\u01B0 kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD sai.`,
    verdict: "B\u1EA3n ho\xE0n thi\u1EC7n nh\u1EA5t c\u1EE7a Bleu de Chanel \u2014 m\u01B0\u1EE3t, \u1EA5m v\xE0 sang. H\u1EE3p ng\u01B0\u1EDDi th\xEDch phong c\xE1ch tr\u01B0\u1EDFng th\xE0nh, l\u1ECBch thi\u1EC7p. \xCDt t\u01B0\u01A1i h\u01A1n EDP nh\u01B0ng b\xF9 l\u1EA1i b\u1EB1ng chi\u1EC1u s\xE2u.",
