    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n ch\u01B0a bao gi\u1EDD ng\u1EEDi hoa hu\u1EC7 (tuberose) th\u1EADt \u2014 th\xEC Carnal Flower c\xF3 th\u1EC3 g\xE2y cho\xE1ng. Dominique Ropion d\xF9ng tuberose absolute t\u1EF1 nhi\xEAn \u1EDF n\u1ED3ng \u0111\u1ED9 c\u1EF1c cao \u2014 m\xF9i hoa tr\u1EAFng \u0111\u1EADm, kem, h\u01A1i indolic (g\u1EA7n m\xF9i da th\u1ECBt). Ai th\xEDch m\xF9i nh\u1EB9 nh\xE0ng, m\xF9i t\u01B0\u01A1i m\xE1t hay m\xF9i g\u1ED7 kh\xF4 s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y n\xF3 M\u1EA0NH v\xE0 "th\u1ECBt" qu\xE1. Gi\xE1 Frederic Malle c\u0169ng thu\u1ED9c top \u0111\u1EAFt nh\u1EA5t niche.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Frederic Malle \u2014 "publisher of perfumes" \u2014 cho perfumer to\xE0n quy\u1EC1n s\xE1ng t\u1EA1o. Dominique Ropion (\u0111\u1EE9ng sau Portrait of a Lady, Oud Satin Mood) t\u1EA1o Carnal Flower nh\u01B0 t\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0111\xE0i tuberose. So v\u1EDBi Tom Ford Tub\xE9reuse Nue \u2014 c\xF9ng tuberose niche \u2014 th\xEC Carnal Flower m\u1EA1nh h\u01A1n, t\u1EF1 nhi\xEAn h\u01A1n v\xE0 \xEDt ng\u1ECDt h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi Gucci Bloom \u2014 tuberose designer \u2014 th\xEC Carnal Flower l\xE0 Rolls Royce c\xF2n Bloom l\xE0 Toyota. B\xE1m 8-10 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa m\u1EA1nh.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

S\u1EF1 ki\u1EC7n quan tr\u1ECDng, opera, tri\u1EC3n l\xE3m, ho\u1EB7c khi mu\u1ED1n m\xF9i h\u01B0\u01A1ng l\xE0 statement. X\u1ECBt 1-2 nh\xE1t SAU C\u1ED4 \u2014 v\xEC EDP m\u1EA1nh. D\xF9ng quanh n\u0103m nh\u01B0ng \u0111\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t m\xF9a \u1EA5m \u2014 tuberose n\u1EDF ra d\u01B0\u1EDBi n\u1EAFng. C\u1EA3 S\xE0i G\xF2n v\xE0 H\xE0 N\u1ED9i \u0111\u1EC1u d\xF9ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c v\xEC b\u1EA1ch \u0111\xE0n gi\u1EEF t\u01B0\u01A1i.`,
