    description: "Clone Creed Aventus n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng nh\u1EA5t \u2014 citrus, tr\xE1i c\xE2y, kh\xF3i v\xE0 da thu\u1ED9c. Gi\xE1 m\u1EC1m nh\u01B0ng hi\u1EC7u n\u0103ng r\u1EA5t m\u1EA1nh. H\u1EE3p ng\u01B0\u1EDDi mu\u1ED1n m\xF9i Aventus m\xE0 kh\xF4ng t\u1ED1n qu\xE1 nhi\u1EC1u.",
    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n \u0111\xE3 c\xF3 Creed Aventus ch\xEDnh h\xE3ng th\xEC CDNIM s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng mang l\u1EA1i g\xEC m\u1EDBi \u2014 n\xF3 l\xE0 phi\xEAn b\u1EA3n l\u1EA5y c\u1EA3m h\u1EE9ng t\u1EEB Aventus \u1EDF t\u1EA7m gi\xE1 r\u1EBB h\u01A1n. Ai nh\u1EA1y m\u0169i s\u1EBD nh\u1EADn ra l\u1EDBp m\u1EDF \u0111\u1EA7u kh\xE1 g\u1EAFt so v\u1EDBi b\u1EA3n g\u1ED1c \u2014 citrus + h\xF3a ch\u1EA5t h\u01A1i s\u1EAFc trong 15-20 ph\xFAt \u0111\u1EA7u. Ngo\xE0i ra, n\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n th\xEDch m\xF9i ng\u1ECDt \u1EA5m ki\u1EC3u gourmand ho\u1EB7c thu \u0111\xF4ng th\xEC CDNIM kh\xF4ng theo h\u01B0\u1EDBng \u0111\xF3 \u2014 \u0111\xE2y l\xE0 m\xF9i fresh-smoky thi\xEAn ban ng\xE0y.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

\u0110\xE2y l\xE0 l\u1EE3i th\u1EBF l\u1EDBn nh\u1EA5t c\u1EE7a CDNIM: gi\xE1 ch\u1EC9 b\u1EB1ng 1/8-1/10 Creed Aventus m\xE0 cho hi\u1EC7u n\u0103ng t\u01B0\u01A1ng \u0111\u01B0\u01A1ng ho\u1EB7c h\u01A1n \u2014 b\xE1m 8 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa m\u1EA1nh. So v\u1EDBi Aventus, CDNIM g\u1EAFt h\u01A1n \u1EDF \u0111\u1EA7u nh\u01B0ng dry down kh\xE1 g\u1EA7n. So v\u1EDBi Afnan 9PM c\xF9ng ph\xE2n kh\xFAc Arab, CDNIM kh\xE1c ho\xE0n to\xE0n v\xEC thi\xEAn fresh-citrus thay v\xEC ng\u1ECDt \u1EA5m. N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n th\xEDch phong c\xE1ch Aventus m\xE0 ch\u01B0a s\u1EB5n s\xE0ng \u0111\u1EA7u t\u01B0 fullbox Creed, CDNIM l\xE0 l\u1EF1a ch\u1ECDn th\u1EF1c d\u1EE5ng nh\u1EA5t.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

D\xF9ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c quanh n\u0103m \u2014 \u0111i l\xE0m, \u0111i ch\u01A1i, g\u1EB7p g\u1EE1. \u0110\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t ban ng\xE0y v\xE0 tr\u1EDDi \u1EA5m (25-32\xB0C). X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t: 1 sau g\xE1y, 1 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc ng\u1EF1c, 1 c\u1ED5 tay. T\u1ECFa r\u1EA5t m\u1EA1nh n\xEAn \u0111\u1EEBng x\u1ECBt qu\xE1 nhi\u1EC1u trong ph\xF2ng k\xEDn. M\xF9a xu\xE2n v\xE0 h\xE8 l\xE0 l\xFAc CDNIM t\u1ECFa \u0111\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t. Bu\u1ED5i t\u1ED1i c\u0169ng OK nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng \u0111\u1EB9p b\u1EB1ng ban ng\xE0y.`,
    verdict: "Clone Aventus gi\xE1 m\u1EC1m \u2014 citrus, tr\xE1i c\xE2y, kh\xF3i r\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7u qu\u1EA3. L\u1EDBp \u0111\u1EA7u h\u01A1i g\u1EAFt nh\u01B0ng dry down r\u1EA5t \u0111\xE1ng. T\u1ED1t nh\u1EA5t cho ng\u01B0\u1EDDi mu\u1ED1n th\u1EED phong c\xE1ch Aventus m\xE0 kh\xF4ng t\u1ED1n qu\xE1 nhi\u1EC1u.",
