    description: "Chai n\u1EEF oriental gia v\u1ECB-hoa-h\u1ED5 ph\xE1ch ki\u1EC3u Gabrielle Chanel \u2014 hoa h\u1ED3ng Bulgaria, rau m\xF9i, \u0111\xE0o, nh\xE0i, cam qu\xFDt, \u0111inh h\u01B0\u01A1ng, h\u1ED3ng, mimosa, hoa cam, c\u1ECF ba l\xE1, h\u1ED5 ph\xE1ch, g\u1ED7 \u0111\xE0n h\u01B0\u01A1ng, \u0111\u1EADu Tonka, vani v\xE0 labdanum. Ph\u1EE9c t\u1EA1p, gi\xE0u v\xE0 r\u1EA5t Chanel.",
    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n ngh\u0129 Chanel = No.5 nh\u1EB9 nh\xE0ng th\xEC Coco EDP s\u1EBD l\xE0 surprise: \u0111\xE2y l\xE0 chai Chanel N\u1EEE N\u1EB6NG NH\u1EA4T \u2014 gia v\u1ECB (\u0111inh h\u01B0\u01A1ng, rau m\xF9i), hoa \u0111\u1EADm (h\u1ED3ng, nh\xE0i), v\xE0 base h\u1ED5 ph\xE1ch-vani-labdanum d\xE0y. Chai l\u1EA5y c\u1EA3m h\u1EE9ng t\u1EEB b\u1ED9 s\u01B0u t\u1EADp ngh\u1EC7 thu\u1EADt \xC1 \u0110\xF4ng c\u1EE7a Gabrielle Chanel. Ai th\xEDch m\xF9i tr\u1EBB trung, nh\u1EB9 nh\xE0ng, t\u01B0\u01A1i m\xE1t s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y Coco qu\xE1 "b\xE0".

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Gi\xE1 Chanel \u2014 v\xE0 Coco EDP l\xE0 chai oriental c\u1ED5 \u0111i\u1EC3n 40+ n\u0103m. Jacques Polge t\u1EA1o ra phi\xEAn b\u1EA3n EDP ph\u1EE9c t\u1EA1p h\u01A1n EDT g\u1ED1c. So v\u1EDBi Coco Noir \u2014 c\xF9ng Chanel \u2014 th\xEC Coco EDP nhi\u1EC1u gia v\u1ECB h\u01A1n, \u1EA5m h\u01A1n, \xEDt t\u1ED1i h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi Guerlain Shalimar \u2014 c\xF9ng nh\xF3m oriental n\u1EEF kinh \u0111i\u1EC3n \u2014 th\xEC Coco nhi\u1EC1u hoa h\u01A1n, \xEDt smoky h\u01A1n. B\xE1m 8-10 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa t\u1ED1t.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

S\u1EF1 ki\u1EC7n trang tr\u1ECDng, opera, ti\u1EC7c t\u1ED1i, ho\u1EB7c khi mu\u1ED1n M\xD9I H\u01AF\u01A0NG C\xD3 TR\u1ECCNG L\u01AF\u1EE2NG. X\u1ECBt 2 nh\xE1t: c\u1ED5 v\xE0 c\u1ED5 tay \u2014 EDP m\u1EA1nh. Thu \u0111\xF4ng \u0111\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t. H\xE0 N\u1ED9i th\xE1ng 10-2. S\xE0i G\xF2n t\u1ED1i m\xE1y l\u1EA1nh. Chai d\xE0nh cho ph\u1EE5 n\u1EEF bi\u1EBFt m\xECnh mu\u1ED1n g\xEC.`,
    verdict: "Oriental n\u1EEF n\u1EB7ng nh\u1EA5t Chanel \u2014 gia v\u1ECB, hoa, h\u1ED5 ph\xE1ch. L\u1EA5y c\u1EA3m h\u1EE9ng \xC1 \u0110\xF4ng. 40+ n\u0103m kh\xF4ng l\u1ED7i m\u1ED1t.",
