    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n \u0111\xE3 c\xF3 Coco EDP \u2014 h\xE3y bi\u1EBFt EDT nh\u1EB9 h\u01A1n R\u1EA4T NHI\u1EC0U. C\xF9ng DNA gia v\u1ECB-hoa-h\u1ED5 ph\xE1ch nh\u01B0ng EDT m\u1ECFng h\u01A1n, t\u1ECFa g\u1EA7n h\u01A1n, b\xE1m ng\u1EAFn h\u01A1n (5-6 gi\u1EDD so v\u1EDBi 9 gi\u1EDD EDP). N\u1EBFu mu\u1ED1n full Coco experience, ch\u1ECDn EDP. EDT ph\xF9 h\u1EE3p h\u01A1n ai th\u1EA5y EDP qu\xE1 n\u1EB7ng ho\u1EB7c mu\u1ED1n d\xF9ng ban ng\xE0y. Gen Z th\xEDch m\xF9i nh\u1EB9 t\u01B0\u01A1i c\u0169ng s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y EDT v\u1EABn "mature" qu\xE1.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Gi\xE1 Chanel \u2014 EDT r\u1EBB h\u01A1n EDP ch\xFAt. V\u1EA5n \u0111\u1EC1 l\xE0: EDT b\xE1m y\u1EBFu, c\u1EA7n x\u1ECBt l\u1EA1i sau 4-5 gi\u1EDD. So v\u1EDBi Coco EDP \u2014 c\xF9ng DNA \u2014 th\xEC EDT nh\u1EB9 h\u01A1n, ph\xF9 h\u1EE3p ng\xE0y \u1EA5m h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi Coco Mademoiselle EDT \u2014 tr\u1EBB h\u01A1n, hi\u1EC7n \u0111\u1EA1i h\u01A1n \u2014 th\xEC Coco EDT c\u1ED5 \u0111i\u1EC3n h\u01A1n, gia v\u1ECB h\u01A1n, \xEDt citrus h\u01A1n.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

Ban ng\xE0y thu nh\u1EB9, \u0111i \u0103n tr\u01B0a, ho\u1EB7c khi mu\u1ED1n Coco m\xE0 kh\xF4ng qu\xE1 n\u1EB7ng. X\u1ECBt 3-4 nh\xE1t v\xEC EDT nh\u1EB9: c\u1ED5, ng\u1EF1c, c\u1ED5 tay. D\xF9ng thu \u0111\xF4ng \u2014 H\xE0 N\u1ED9i th\xE1ng 10-3. S\xE0i G\xF2n ban ng\xE0y ph\xF2ng \u0111i\u1EC1u h\xF2a. N\u1EBFu ch\u01B0a th\u1EED Coco, n\xEAn b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u t\u1EEB EDT r\u1ED3i quy\u1EBFt EDP sau.`,
