    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n quen v\u1EDBi Chanel No.5 ho\u1EB7c Chance \u2014 nh\u1EB9, s\xE1ng, ph\u1EA5n \u2014 th\xEC Coco Noir s\u1EBD ho\xE0n to\xE0n l\xE0 m\u1ED9t Chanel kh\xE1c. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 chai T\u1ED0I nh\u1EA5t trong collection: ho\u1EAFc h\u01B0\u01A1ng, tr\u1EA7m h\u01B0\u01A1ng v\xE0 vani \u0111\xE8 l\xEAn hoa h\u1ED3ng-nh\xE0i, t\u1EA1o ra m\xF9i "nguy hi\u1EC3m" thay v\xEC "d\u1EC5 th\u01B0\u01A1ng". N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n mua chai Chanel \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EB7c \u0111i brunch Ch\u1EE7 nh\u1EADt, th\xEC kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i chai n\xE0y. Coco Noir l\xE0 chai b\u1EA1n d\xF9ng khi mu\u1ED1n khi\u1EBFn ai \u0111\xF3 kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 qu\xEAn m\xECnh.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Gi\xE1 Chanel \u2014 kh\xF4ng r\u1EBB, nh\u01B0ng Coco Noir \xEDt khi gi\u1EA3m gi\xE1 v\xEC Chanel kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD b\xE1n nh\u01B0 v\u1EADy. So v\u1EDBi Chanel Chance Eau Tendre \u2014 c\xF9ng h\xE3ng nh\u01B0ng kh\xE1c ho\xE0n to\xE0n \u2014 th\xEC Coco Noir t\u1ED1i h\u01A1n, \u0111\u1EADm h\u01A1n v\xE0 tr\u01B0\u1EDFng th\xE0nh h\u01A1n r\u1EA5t nhi\u1EC1u. So v\u1EDBi YSL Black Opium \u2014 c\xF9ng nh\xF3m n\u1EEF t\u1ED1i \u2014 th\xEC Coco Noir \xEDt ng\u1ECDt h\u01A1n, nhi\u1EC1u tr\u1EA7m h\u01B0\u01A1ng h\u01A1n v\xE0 ki\u1EC3u "\u0111\u1EAFt" h\u01A1n. B\xE1m 7-8 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa v\u1EEBa.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

\u0110i \u0103n t\u1ED1i \u1EDF nh\xE0 h\xE0ng, d\u1EF1 s\u1EF1 ki\u1EC7n bu\u1ED5i t\u1ED1i, ho\u1EB7c khi mu\u1ED1n m\u1EB7c \u0111\u1ED3 \u0111en ra ngo\xE0i. X\u1ECBt 2 nh\xE1t sau c\u1ED5 v\xE0 c\u1ED5 tay. \u0110\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t thu \u0111\xF4ng \u2014 H\xE0 N\u1ED9i th\xE1ng 10-2 l\xE0 l\xFD t\u01B0\u1EDFng. \u1EDE S\xE0i G\xF2n th\xEC d\xF9ng t\u1ED1i, ph\xF2ng m\xE1y l\u1EA1nh. Tr\xE1nh ban ng\xE0y n\xF3ng v\xEC ho\u1EAFc h\u01B0\u01A1ng s\u1EBD n\u1EB7ng.`,
