    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n th\xEDch m\xF9i m\u1EA1nh, ng\u1ECDt, hay sexy \u2014 th\xEC Diorissimo s\u1EBD qu\xE1 nh\u1EB9, qu\xE1 "tr\u1EAFng", qu\xE1 innocent. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 hoa linh lan (lily of the valley) \u2014 lo\xE0i hoa m\xE0 Dior y\xEAu nh\u1EA5t \u2014 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c Edmond Roudnitska, m\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng perfumer V\u0128 \u0110\u1EA0I NH\u1EA4T l\u1ECBch s\u1EED, t\xE1i hi\u1EC7n tr\xEAn da. M\xF9i nh\u01B0 WI s\xE1ng \u0111\u1EA7u xu\xE2n \u2014 s\u1EA1ch, xanh, t\u01B0\u01A1i \u2014 kh\xF4ng c\xF3 g\xEC n\u1EB7ng n\u1EC1.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Gi\xE1 Dior t\u1EA7m trung \u2014 nh\u01B0ng Diorissimo thu\u1ED9c d\xF2ng heritage, ra \u0111\u1EDDi 1956. Edmond Roudnitska (perfumer c\u0169ng t\u1EA1o Eau Sauvage) l\xE0 legend \u2014 v\xE0 Diorissimo \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c coi l\xE0 KI\u1EC6T T\xC1C soliflore linh lan. V\u1EA5n \u0111\u1EC1: hoa linh lan kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 chi\u1EBFt xu\u1EA5t t\u1EF1 nhi\xEAn \u2014 n\xEAn to\xE0n b\u1ED9 l\xE0 art of synthesis. So v\u1EDBi Guerlain Muguet \u2014 c\xF9ng linh lan \u2014 th\xEC Diorissimo s\u1EA1ch h\u01A1n, \xEDt ph\u1EA5n h\u01A1n. B\xE1m 4-5 gi\u1EDD (EDT nh\u1EB9).

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

M\xF9a xu\xE2n, ban ng\xE0y, \u0111i d\u1EA1o, d\u1EF1 l\u1EC5, ho\u1EB7c khi mu\u1ED1n m\xF9i h\u01B0\u01A1ng thu\u1EA7n khi\u1EBFt nh\u1EA5t. X\u1ECBt 3-4 nh\xE1t v\xEC EDT nh\u1EB9. \u0110\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t th\xE1ng 3-5 \u2014 khi hoa th\u1EADt s\u1EF1 n\u1EDF. C\u1EA3 S\xE0i G\xF2n v\xE0 H\xE0 N\u1ED9i d\xF9ng ban ng\xE0y. Chai d\xE0nh cho ai hi\u1EC3u r\u1EB1ng \u0111\u01A1n gi\u1EA3n l\xE0 \u0111\u1EC9nh cao.`,
    verdict: "Linh lan thu\u1EA7n khi\u1EBFt \u2014 Roudnitska 1956. Ki\u1EC7t t\xE1c soliflore. \u0110\u01A1n gi\u1EA3n nh\u01B0ng \u0111\u1EC9nh cao n\u01B0\u1EDBc hoa.",
