    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n d\u01B0\u1EDBi 30 \u2014 th\xEC Drakkar Noir s\u1EBD l\xE0 m\xF9i BA b\u1EA1n x\u1ECBt h\u1ED3i th\u1EADp ni\xEAn 90. V\xE0 \u0111\xFAng v\u1EADy: \u0111\xE2y t\u1EEBng l\xE0 chai nam B\xC1N CH\u1EA0Y NH\u1EA4T th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi su\u1ED1t th\u1EADp ni\xEAn 80-90, tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi Acqua di Gio thay th\u1EBF. Foug\xE8re t\u1ED1i: o\u1EA3i h\u01B0\u01A1ng, r\xEAu s\u1ED3i, da, nh\u1EF1a \u2014 \u0111\u1EADm, n\u1EB7ng, kh\xF4ng c\xF3 g\xEC synthetic. Ai quen m\xF9i hi\u1EC7n \u0111\u1EA1i s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y n\xF3 qu\xE1 old school.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Gi\xE1 \u2014 C\u1EF0C R\u1EBA. R\u1EBB h\u01A1n CK Obsession, r\u1EBB h\u01A1n g\u1EA7n nh\u01B0 m\u1ECDi th\u1EE9. V\xE0 v\u1EDBi m\u1ED9t chai \u0111\xE3 b\xE1n h\xE0ng tri\u1EC7u chai kh\u1EAFp th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi, t\u1EEBng l\xE0 bi\u1EC3u t\u01B0\u1EE3ng nam t\xEDnh th\u1EADp ni\xEAn 80-90, gi\xE1 n\xE0y l\xE0 steal. So v\u1EDBi Polo Green \u2014 c\xF9ng era \u2014 th\xEC Drakkar Noir t\u1ED1i h\u01A1n, \xEDt xanh h\u01A1n, nhi\u1EC1u da h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi Sauvage \u2014 c\xF9ng ambroxan era hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i \u2014 th\xEC Drakkar l\xE0 antonym: t\u1ED1i vs s\xE1ng, n\u1EB7ng vs nh\u1EB9. B\xE1m 6-7 gi\u1EDD.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

M\xF9a \u0111\xF4ng, bu\u1ED5i t\u1ED1i, ho\u1EB7c khi mu\u1ED1n th\u1EED tr\u1EA3i nghi\u1EC7m "m\xF9i c\u1EE7a m\u1ED9t th\u1EDDi \u0111\u1EA1i". X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t: c\u1ED5 v\xE0 ng\u1EF1c. H\xE0 N\u1ED9i th\xE1ng 11-2. S\xE0i G\xF2n kh\xF3 d\xF9ng do n\xF3ng. Chai \u0111\u1EC3 hi\u1EC3u l\u1ECBch s\u1EED n\u01B0\u1EDBc hoa nam.`,
