    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n mu\u1ED1n m\xF9i hoa r\xF5 r\xE0ng ki\u1EC3u rose hay jasmine \u2014 th\xEC Dune s\u1EBD khi\u1EBFn b\u1EA1n b\u1ED1i r\u1ED1i v\xEC n\xF3 ABSTRACT. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 m\xF9i C\xC1T \u2014 kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i c\xE1t bi\u1EC3n t\u01B0\u01A1i m\xE1t, m\xE0 c\xE1t sa m\u1EA1c \u1EA5m d\u01B0\u1EDBi n\u1EAFng chi\u1EC1u, c\xF3 h\u01A1i bi\u1EC3n bay v\xE0o. R\u1EA5t kh\xF3 m\xF4 t\u1EA3 = r\u1EA5t kh\xF3 b\xE1n. Nh\u01B0ng ai \u0111\xE3 hi\u1EC3u th\xEC s\u1EBD y\xEAu. Dominique Ropion tham gia nh\xF3m perfumer \u2014 c\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi t\u1EA1o Carnal Flower.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Gi\xE1 Dior t\u1EA7m trung \u2014 nh\u01B0ng Dune ra \u0111\u1EDDi 1991, thu\u1ED9c nh\xF3m heritage. 3 perfumer h\u1EE3p t\xE1c t\u1EA1o ra th\u1EE9 g\xEC \u0111\xF3 m\xE0 \u0111\u1EBFn gi\u1EDD ch\u01B0a ai replicate \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c: m\xF9i c\xE1t \u1EA5m. So v\u1EDBi Herm\xE8s Terre d'Herm\xE8s \u2014 c\xF9ng nh\xF3m \u0111\u1EA5t-kho\xE1ng \u2014 th\xEC Dune n\u1EEF h\u01A1n, nhi\u1EC1u h\u1ED5 ph\xE1ch h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi CK Eternity \u2014 c\xF9ng 90s n\u1EEF \u2014 th\xEC Dune abstract h\u01A1n, kh\xF3 ti\u1EBFp c\u1EADn h\u01A1n nh\u01B0ng th\xFA v\u1ECB h\u01A1n. B\xE1m 6-7 gi\u1EDD.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

Cu\u1ED1i tu\u1EA7n th\u01B0 gi\xE3n, \u0111i bi\u1EC3n, d\u1EA1o ho\xE0ng h\xF4n, ho\u1EB7c khi mu\u1ED1n m\xF9i h\u01B0\u01A1ng m\xE0 kh\xF4ng ai h\u1ECFi "x\u1ECBt m\xF9i g\xEC" m\xE0 h\u1ECFi "c\u1EA3m gi\xE1c g\xEC th\u1EBF?". X\u1ECBt 3 nh\xE1t: c\u1ED5 v\xE0 c\u1ED5 tay. D\xF9ng quanh n\u0103m \u2014 c\xE1t \u1EA5m v\xE0o \u0111\xF4ng, bi\u1EC3n t\u01B0\u01A1i v\xE0o h\xE8. Chai d\xE0nh cho dreamer.`,
