    description: "Chai n\u1EEF hoa h\u1ED3ng kinh \u0111i\u1EC3n \u2014 m\u1EABu \u0111\u01A1n, v\u1EA3i, hoa h\u1ED3ng v\xE0 g\u1ED7 tuy\u1EBFt t\xF9ng. Thanh l\u1ECBch, n\u1EEF t\xEDnh v\xE0 r\u1EA5t tinh kh\xF4i. Chai signature l\xFD t\u01B0\u1EDFng cho m\u1ECDi ng\xE0y.",
    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n th\xEDch m\xF9i ng\u1ECDt \u0111\u1EADm, sexy ho\u1EB7c gourmand th\xEC Chlo\xE9 EDP s\u1EBD qu\xE1 nh\u1EB9 v\xE0 qu\xE1 thanh l\u1ECBch cho gu \u0111\xF3. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 m\xF9i hoa h\u1ED3ng ph\u1EA5n clean \u2014 r\u1EA5t elegant nh\u01B0ng thi\u1EBFu drama. Ai c\u1EA7n m\xF9i t\u1EA1o d\u1EA5u \u1EA5n m\u1EA1nh, t\u1ECFa xa c\u0169ng s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y Chlo\xE9 h\u01A1i k\xEDn \u0111\xE1o. Ngo\xE0i ra, nam gi\u1EDBi mu\u1ED1n mua t\u1EB7ng b\u1EA1n g\xE1i n\xEAn ch\xFA \xFD: Chlo\xE9 EDP kh\xE1 mature \u2014 ph\xF9 h\u1EE3p ph\u1EE5 n\u1EEF 25+ h\u01A1n l\xE0 teen.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Chlo\xE9 EDP thu\u1ED9c ph\xE2n kh\xFAc designer t\u1EA7m trung \u2014 r\u1EBB h\u01A1n Coco Mademoiselle v\xE0 Chanel. So v\u1EDBi Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet, Chlo\xE9 EDP \u0111\u1EADm h\u01A1n, hoa h\u1ED3ng r\xF5 h\u01A1n v\xE0 n\u1EEF t\xEDnh tr\u01B0\u1EDFng th\xE0nh h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi Lanc\xF4me La Vie Est Belle, Chlo\xE9 EDP \xEDt ng\u1ECDt h\u01A1n nhi\u1EC1u v\xE0 thanh h\u01A1n. Hi\u1EC7u n\u0103ng kh\xE1: b\xE1m 6-7 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa v\u1EEBa. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 chai signature n\u1EEF kinh \u0111i\u1EC3n \u2014 hoa h\u1ED3ng ph\u1EA5n m\xE0 g\u1EA7n nh\u01B0 kh\xF4ng ai gh\xE9t.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

D\xF9ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c quanh n\u0103m \u2014 \u0111i l\xE0m, \u0111i c\xE0 ph\xEA, g\u1EB7p g\u1EE1, \u0111i ti\u1EC7c nh\u1EB9. X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t: c\u1ED5, c\u1ED5 tay, sau tai. \u0110\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t m\xF9a xu\xE2n h\xE8 khi tr\u1EDDi \u1EA5m. \u1EDE S\xE0i G\xF2n d\xF9ng tho\u1EA3i m\xE1i v\xEC r\u1EA5t nh\u1EB9 nh\xE0ng. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 ki\u1EC3u chai ph\u1EE5 n\u1EEF n\xE0o d\xF9ng c\u0169ng th\u1EA5y h\u1EE3p \u2014 tinh t\u1EBF, thanh l\u1ECBch v\xE0 r\u1EA5t ladylike.`,
    verdict: "M\xF9i hoa h\u1ED3ng ph\u1EA5n thanh l\u1ECBch \u2014 kinh \u0111i\u1EC3n v\xE0 r\u1EA5t n\u1EEF t\xEDnh. H\u1EE3p m\u1ECDi ng\xE0y. Kh\xF4ng h\u1EE3p ai th\xEDch m\xF9i n\u1EB7ng, sexy hay ng\u1ECDt \u0111\u1EADm.",
