    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n quen m\xF9i Sauvage EDP hay Bleu de Chanel \u2014 c\xE1c chai t\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EA1ch, d\u1EC5 ch\u1ECBu, ai x\u1ECBt c\u0169ng khen \u2014 th\xEC Fahrenheit s\u1EBD g\xE2y s\u1ED1c. M\xF9i x\u0103ng, da v\xE0 hoa t\xEDm ph\u1EA3 v\xE0o m\u1EB7t ngay ph\xFAt \u0111\u1EA7u, nhi\u1EC1u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1EBD h\u1ECFi "anh v\u1EEBa \u0111\u1ED5 x\u0103ng \xE0?". Kh\xF4ng n\xEAn x\u1ECBt \u0111i ph\u1ECFng v\u1EA5n, h\u1ECDp kh\xE1ch h\xE0ng, ho\u1EB7c b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 ch\u1ED7 n\xE0o c\u1EA7n g\xE2y thi\u1EC7n c\u1EA3m l\u1EA7n \u0111\u1EA7u. Anh em d\u01B0\u1EDBi 25 tu\u1ED5i ph\u1EA7n l\u1EDBn s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y n\xF3 gi\xE0, v\xEC th\u1EADt ra Fahrenheit ra \u0111\u1EDDi n\u0103m 1988 v\xE0 thu\u1ED9c v\u1EC1 th\u1EBF h\u1EC7 cha ch\xFA.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Fahrenheit gi\xE1 ch\u1EC9 b\u1EB1ng n\u1EEDa Tom Ford Tuscan Leather \u2014 m\xE0 m\xF9i da kh\xF4ng thua k\xE9m l\xE0 bao. Chai n\xE0y r\u1EBB nh\u1EA5t trong lineup Dior nam, nh\u01B0ng ch\u1EA5t li\u1EC7u da v\xE0 hoa t\xEDm b\xEAn trong th\xEC kh\xF4ng chai designer n\xE0o kh\xE1c c\xF3. N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n \u0111\xE3 t\u1EEBng ng\u1EEDi Tuscan Leather v\xE0 th\xEDch nh\u01B0ng s\u1EE3 gi\xE1, th\xEC n\xEAn th\u1EED Fahrenheit tr\u01B0\u1EDBc. L\u01B0u \xFD l\xE0 EDT n\xEAn t\u1ECFa h\u01B0\u01A1ng kh\xF4ng qu\xE1 m\u1EA1nh \u2014 t\u1EA7m 5-6 gi\u1EDD, v\xF2ng tay tr\u1EDF v\xE0o. Nh\u01B0ng v\u1EDBi gi\xE1 n\xE0y th\xEC x\u1ECBt th\xEAm nh\xE1t bu\u1ED5i chi\u1EC1u c\u0169ng ch\u1EB3ng ti\u1EBFc.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

\u0110i ch\u01A1i cu\u1ED1i tu\u1EA7n, \u0111i bar, xem nh\u1EA1c s\u1ED1ng, ho\u1EB7c ch\u1EA1y xe chi\u1EC1u t\u1ED1i tr\u1EDDi m\xE1t. X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t tr\u01B0\u1EDBc ng\u1EF1c v\xE0 sau c\u1ED5. Tr\u1EDDi H\xE0 N\u1ED9i th\xE1ng 11-12, kho\xE1c \xE1o kho\xE1c da r\u1ED3i x\u1ECBt Fahrenheit l\xEAn c\u1ED5 \xE1o \u2014 \u0111\xF3 l\xE0 l\xFAc n\xF3 \u0111\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t. \u1EDE S\xE0i G\xF2n th\xEC t\u1ED1i m\xE1t ho\u1EB7c ph\xF2ng m\xE1y l\u1EA1nh m\u1EDBi n\xEAn d\xF9ng. Kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i chai h\u1EB1ng ng\xE0y, nh\u01B0ng khi \u0111\xFAng l\xFAc th\xEC kh\xF4ng g\xEC thay \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c.`,
