    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n gh\xE9t m\xF9i ng\u1ECDt tr\xE1i c\xE2y th\xEC Burberry Her s\u1EBD qu\xE1 ng\u1ECDt \u2014 berry \u0111\u1ECF (d\xE2u, m\xE2m x\xF4i, blackberry) ph\u1EA3 ra ngay ph\xFAt \u0111\u1EA7u, g\u1EA7n nh\u01B0 ki\u1EC3u k\u1EB9o d\xE2u. Ai th\xEDch m\xF9i thanh l\u1ECBch ki\u1EC3u Chanel hay m\xF9i powdery mature c\u0169ng s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y Her qu\xE1 tr\u1EBB v\xE0 qu\xE1 "candy". Ngo\xE0i ra, chai nh\u1ECF nh\u1EA5t (50ml) kh\xF4ng r\u1EBB cho m\xF9i ng\u1ECDt d\xE2u \u2014 n\u1EBFu ch\u01B0a ch\u1EAFc th\xEC n\xEAn th\u1EED chi\u1EBFt 10ml tr\u01B0\u1EDBc.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

B\u1EA5t ng\u1EDD: ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\u1EE9ng sau Burberry Her l\xE0 Francis Kurkdjian \u2014 perfumer t\u1EA1o ra BR540 v\xE0 Baccarat Rouge. Chai n\xE0y r\u1EBB h\u01A1n MFK 4-5 l\u1EA7n nh\u01B0ng c\xF3 chi\u1EC1u s\xE2u t\u01B0\u01A1ng t\u1EF1 \u1EDF ph\u1EA7n base: cashmeran, vani v\xE0 x\u1EA1 h\u01B0\u01A1ng t\u1EA1o l\u1EDBp kem \u1EA5m ph\xEDa d\u01B0\u1EDBi berry. So v\u1EDBi Sol de Janeiro Cheirosa 62 \u2014 c\xF9ng nh\xF3m ng\u1ECDt-\u1EA5m \u2014 th\xEC Her ph\u1EE9c t\u1EA1p h\u01A1n v\u1EDBi violet-jasmine \u1EDF gi\u1EEFa. So v\u1EDBi Ariana Grande Cloud \u2014 c\xF9ng ng\u1ECDt tr\u1EBB \u2014 th\xEC Her berry h\u01A1n v\xE0 \xEDt marshmallow h\u01A1n. B\xE1m 6-7 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa v\u1EEBa.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

\u0110i cafe, \u0111i shopping, g\u1EB7p b\u1EA1n b\xE8, h\u1EB9n h\xF2 casual. X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t c\u1ED5 v\xE0 c\u1ED5 tay. D\xF9ng quanh n\u0103m \u2014 \u1EDF S\xE0i G\xF2n d\xF9ng tho\u1EA3i m\xE1i v\xEC berry t\u01B0\u01A1i s\xE1ng. H\xE0 N\u1ED9i m\xF9a \u0111\xF4ng th\xEC cashmeran-vani \u1EA5m l\xEAn \u0111\u1EB9p. Chai n\xE0y t\u1ECFa h\u01B0\u01A1ng vui v\u1EBB \u2014 ai \u0111\u1EE9ng g\u1EA7n c\u0169ng th\u1EA5y tho\u1EA3i m\xE1i.`,
