    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n ch\u1EC9 c\u1EA7n chai d\u1EC5 d\xF9ng h\u1EB1ng ng\xE0y ki\u1EC3u Sauvage hay Bleu de Chanel th\xEC Noir Extreme s\u1EBD qu\xE1 \u1EA5m, qu\xE1 t\u1ED1i v\xE0 qu\xE1 "k\u1ECBch" cho m\u1EE5c \u0111\xEDch \u0111\xF3. Ai \u0111i l\xE0m v\u0103n ph\xF2ng gi\u1EEFa tr\u01B0a n\xF3ng c\u0169ng n\xEAn tr\xE1nh \u2014 chai n\xE0y t\u1ECFa h\u01A1i d\xE0y, ng\u1ECDt \u1EA5m, kh\xF4ng h\u1EE3p kh\xF4ng gian k\xEDn n\xF3ng. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi m\u1EDBi ch\u01A1i n\u01B0\u1EDBc hoa c\xF3 th\u1EC3 th\u1EA5y n\xF3 h\u01A1i "gi\xE0" so v\u1EDBi k\u1EF3 v\u1ECDng.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Gi\xE1 Tom Ford thu\u1ED9c ph\xE2n kh\xFAc designer cao c\u1EA5p \u2014 \u0111\u1EAFt h\u01A1n Dior, Chanel r\xF5 r\u1EC7t. Nh\u01B0ng Noir Extreme c\xF3 c\xE1i m\xE0 \xEDt chai designer n\xE0o c\xF3: c\u1EA3m gi\xE1c "niche" trong v\u1ECF designer. So v\u1EDBi Valentino Uomo Intense (c\u0169ng \u1EA5m vani), Noir Extreme ph\u1EE9c t\u1EA1p h\u01A1n nh\u1EDD l\u1EDBp gia v\u1ECB kulfi v\xE0 ngh\u1EC7 t\xE2y. So v\u1EDBi Spicebomb Extreme (Viktor & Rolf), Noir Extreme sang h\u01A1n v\xE0 \xEDt k\u1EB9o h\u01A1n. B\xE1m 8 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa t\u1ED1t. Gi\xE1 cao nh\u01B0ng x\u1EE9ng \u0111\xE1ng cho ai d\xF9ng \u0111\xFAng ho\xE0n c\u1EA3nh.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

Bu\u1ED5i t\u1ED1i, h\u1EB9n h\xF2, ti\u1EC7c, s\u1EF1 ki\u1EC7n ho\u1EB7c tr\u1EDDi m\xE1t. X\u1ECBt 2 nh\xE1t: c\u1ED5 v\xE0 ng\u1EF1c. \u0110\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t thu-\u0111\xF4ng. \u1EDE Vi\u1EC7t Nam h\u1EE3p t\u1ED1i m\xE1t, ph\xF2ng m\xE1y l\u1EA1nh ho\u1EB7c m\xF9a l\u1EA1nh H\xE0 N\u1ED9i. \u0110\u1EEBng d\xF9ng gi\u1EEFa tr\u01B0a n\u1EAFng g\u1EAFt.`,
