    description: "Chai nam nh\xE0i-neroli-iris s\u1EA1ch sang nh\u1EA5t \u2014 h\u01B0\u01A1ng th\u1EA3o, ti\xEAu h\u1ED3ng, petitgrain, nh\xE0i, neroli, iris, g\u1ED7 \u0111\xE0n h\u01B0\u01A1ng, g\u1ED7 tuy\u1EBFt t\xF9ng, c\u1ECF h\u01B0\u01A1ng b\xE0i v\xE0 ho\u1EAFc h\u01B0\u01A1ng. S\u1EA1ch, tr\u1EAFng v\xE0 r\u1EA5t gentlemanly.",
    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n th\xEDch "m\xF9i n\u01B0\u1EDBc hoa nam" ki\u1EC3u m\u1EA1nh m\u1EBD \u2014 oud, da, thu\u1ED1c l\xE1, ho\u1EB7c \xEDt nh\u1EA5t l\xE0 ambroxan t\u1ECFa xa \u2014 th\xEC Reflection Man s\u1EBD khi\u1EBFn b\u1EA1n th\u1EA5t v\u1ECDng. Chai n\xE0y s\u1EA1ch \u0111\u1EBFn m\u1EE9c nhi\u1EC1u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi n\xF3i "nh\u01B0 m\xF9i x\xE0 ph\xF2ng cao c\u1EA5p" \u2014 v\xE0 t\xF9y g\xF3c nh\xECn, \u0111\xF3 l\xE0 khen ho\u1EB7c ch\xEA. Ai c\u1EA7n m\xF9i g\xE2y \u1EA5n t\u01B0\u1EE3ng m\u1EA1nh trong 3 gi\xE2y \u0111\u1EA7u c\u0169ng n\xEAn nh\xECn qua: Reflection Man c\u1EA7n 30 ph\xFAt \u0111\u1EC3 l\u1EAFng xu\u1ED1ng m\u1EDBi \u0111\u1EB9p.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Amouage thu\u1ED9c niche Oman \u2014 \u0111\u1EAFt h\u01A1n designer nh\u01B0ng r\u1EBB h\u01A1n MFK v\xE0 Creed. \u0110i\u1EC1u Reflection Man l\xE0m xu\u1EA5t s\u1EAFc l\xE0 hoa nh\xE0i trong n\u01B0\u1EDBc hoa nam m\xE0 kh\xF4ng b\u1ECB n\u1EEF t\xEDnh \u2014 nh\u1EDD h\u01B0\u01A1ng th\u1EA3o v\xE0 g\u1ED7 \u0111\xE0n h\u01B0\u01A1ng c\xE2n b\u1EB1ng. So v\u1EDBi Dior Homme Intense \u2014 c\xF9ng nh\xF3m hoa-ph\u1EA5n nam \u2014 th\xEC Reflection s\u1EA1ch h\u01A1n, \xEDt iris ph\u1EA5n h\u01A1n v\xE0 nhi\u1EC1u g\u1ED7 h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi Bleu de Chanel \u2014 c\xF9ng nh\xF3m "s\u1EA1ch sang" \u2014 th\xEC Reflection thanh l\u1ECBch h\u01A1n m\u1ED9t t\u1EA7m r\xF5 r\u1EC7t. B\xE1m 7-8 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa nh\u1EB9-v\u1EEBa.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

\u0110i l\xE0m sang tr\u1ECDng, g\u1EB7p kh\xE1ch h\xE0ng quan tr\u1ECDng, \u0111i \u0103n tr\u01B0a \u1EDF nh\xE0 h\xE0ng, ho\u1EB7c b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 khi n\xE0o mu\u1ED1n t\u1EA1o h\xECnh \u1EA3nh ch\u1EC9nh t\u1EC1 m\xE0 kh\xF4ng c\u1EA7n la h\xE9t. X\u1ECBt 3 nh\xE1t: c\u1ED5, ng\u1EF1c, c\u1ED5 tay. D\xF9ng quanh n\u0103m \u2014 S\xE0i G\xF2n hay H\xE0 N\u1ED9i \u0111\u1EC1u tho\u1EA3i m\xE1i v\xEC m\xF9i r\u1EA5t s\u1EA1ch. Tr\xE1nh \u0111i club hay nh\u1EADu \u2014 l\xE3ng ph\xED.`,
