    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n gh\xE9t \u0111\u1EE5ng h\xE0ng th\xEC Sauvage EDP l\xE0 chai \u0111\u1EE5ng nhi\u1EC1u nh\u1EA5t \u2014 v\xEC n\xF3 qu\xE1 ph\u1ED5 bi\u1EBFn. Ai th\xEDch m\xF9i \u0111\u1ED9c l\u1EA1, c\xE1 t\xEDnh ri\xEAng ho\u1EB7c niche s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y Sauvage qu\xE1 an to\xE0n v\xE0 qu\xE1 mainstream. Ngo\xE0i ra, n\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n \u0111\xE3 c\xF3 Sauvage EDT th\xEC EDP kh\xE1 g\u1EA7n \u2014 s\xE2u h\u01A1n, \u1EA5m h\u01A1n nh\u01B0ng DNA gi\u1ED1ng. C\xE2n nh\u1EAFc tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi mua th\xEAm.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Sauvage EDP thu\u1ED9c ph\xE2n kh\xFAc designer cao c\u1EA5p \u2014 gi\xE1 t\u01B0\u01A1ng \u0111\u01B0\u01A1ng Bleu de Chanel EDP. So v\u1EDBi b\u1EA3n EDT, EDP \u1EA5m h\u01A1n, m\u01B0\u1EE3t h\u01A1n v\xE0 b\xE1m t\u1ED1t h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi b\u1EA3n Elixir, EDP nh\u1EB9 h\u01A1n v\xE0 d\u1EC5 d\xF9ng ban ng\xE0y h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi Bleu de Chanel EDP, Sauvage EDP tr\u1EBB h\u01A1n, cay h\u01A1n v\xE0 n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt h\u01A1n. Hi\u1EC7u n\u0103ng r\u1EA5t t\u1ED1t: b\xE1m 8 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa m\u1EA1nh. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 chai \u0111a d\u1EE5ng nh\u1EA5t trong d\xF2ng Sauvage \u2014 n\u1EBFu ch\u1EC9 mua 1, ch\u1ECDn EDP.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

D\xF9ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c quanh n\u0103m \u2014 \u0111i l\xE0m, \u0111i ch\u01A1i, h\u1EB9n h\xF2, g\u1EB7p g\u1EE1. X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t: 1 sau g\xE1y, 1 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc ng\u1EF1c, 1 c\u1ED5 tay. \u0110\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t m\xF9a xu\xE2n thu khi tr\u1EDDi m\xE1t. \u1EDE S\xE0i G\xF2n d\xF9ng ban ng\xE0y trong ph\xF2ng m\xE1y l\u1EA1nh r\u1EA5t tho\u1EA3i m\xE1i. Bu\u1ED5i t\u1ED1i c\u0169ng OK nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng \u0111\u1EB9p b\u1EB1ng Elixir. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 ki\u1EC3u chai x\u1ECBt xong \u0111i lu\xF4n \u2014 g\u1EA7n nh\u01B0 kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD sai.`,
    verdict: "M\xF9i n\xE0y s\u1EA1ch, nam t\xEDnh v\xE0 r\u1EA5t d\u1EC5 d\xF9ng. H\u1EE3p ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\u1EA7n m\u1ED9t chai \u0111a d\u1EE5ng \u0111\u1EC3 d\xF9ng h\u1EB1ng ng\xE0y. Qu\xE1 ph\u1ED5 bi\u1EBFn n\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n mu\u1ED1n s\u1EF1 \u0111\u1ED9c \u0111\xE1o.",
