    article: `### Ai kh\xF4ng n\xEAn mua?

N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n \u0111\xE3 c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u chai designer nam hi\u1EC7n \u0111\u1EA1i ki\u1EC3u Dior Sauvage, Dylan Blue hay Prada Luna Rossa Carbon th\xEC Y EDP s\u1EBD h\u01A1i quen v\xEC c\xF9ng nh\xF3m fresh-ambroxan. Ai th\xEDch m\xF9i \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t, c\xE1 t\xEDnh ri\xEAng ho\u1EB7c theo h\u01B0\u1EDBng niche s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y chai n\xE0y qu\xE1 an to\xE0n v\xE0 thi\u1EBFu chi\u1EC1u s\xE2u. Ngo\xE0i ra, ng\u01B0\u1EDDi gh\xE9t ambroxan (c\xE1i ch\u1EA5t s\u1EA1ch h\u01A1i t\u1ED5ng h\u1EE3p ph\u1ED5 bi\u1EBFn \u1EDF designer \u0111\u1EDDi m\u1EDBi) th\xEC n\xEAn tr\xE1nh.

### C\xF3 \u0111\xE1ng ti\u1EC1n kh\xF4ng?

Y EDP thu\u1ED9c ph\xE2n kh\xFAc designer t\u1EA7m trung \u2014 gi\xE1 m\u1EC1m h\u01A1n Bleu de Chanel hay Dior Sauvage EDP. So v\u1EDBi Bleu de Chanel, Y EDP tr\u1EBB h\u01A1n, t\u01B0\u01A1i h\u01A1n nh\u01B0ng \xEDt s\xE2u h\u01A1n. So v\u1EDBi Sauvage EDP, Y EDP \xEDt n\u1EB7ng h\u01A1n v\xE0 d\u1EC5 d\xF9ng h\u1EB1ng ng\xE0y h\u01A1n. Hi\u1EC7u n\u0103ng kh\xE1 t\u1ED1t cho ph\xE2n kh\xFAc: b\xE1m 7-8 gi\u1EDD, t\u1ECFa r\xF5 trong 3-4 gi\u1EDD \u0111\u1EA7u. N\u1EBFu c\u1EA7n m\u1ED9t chai \u0111a d\u1EE5ng, d\u1EC5 khen v\xE0 kh\xF4ng \u0111\u1EAFt, Y EDP l\xE0 l\u1EF1a ch\u1ECDn r\u1EA5t \u0111\xE1ng c\xE2n nh\u1EAFc. N\xEAn mua chi\u1EBFt 10ml th\u1EED tr\u01B0\u1EDBc.

### N\xEAn d\xF9ng khi n\xE0o?

D\xF9ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c quanh n\u0103m \u2014 \u0111i l\xE0m, \u0111i h\u1ECDc, \u0111i ch\u01A1i, h\u1EB9n h\xF2 nh\u1EB9. X\u1ECBt 2-3 nh\xE1t: 1 sau g\xE1y, 1 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc ng\u1EF1c, 1 c\u1ED5 tay. \u0110\u1EB9p nh\u1EA5t v\xE0o m\xF9a xu\xE2n v\xE0 thu khi tr\u1EDDi m\xE1t (22-28\xB0C). \u1EDE S\xE0i G\xF2n d\xF9ng t\u1ED1t trong ph\xF2ng m\xE1y l\u1EA1nh. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 ki\u1EC3u chai x\u1ECBt xong \u0111i lu\xF4n, kh\xF4ng c\u1EA7n ngh\u0129 nhi\u1EC1u. \u0110\u1EEBng d\xF9ng cho d\u1ECBp quan tr\u1ECDng c\u1EA7n g\xE2y \u1EA5n t\u01B0\u1EE3ng m\u1EA1nh \u2014 Y EDP l\xE0 m\xF9i d\u1EC5 ch\u1ECBu h\u01A1n l\xE0 m\xF9i \u1EA5n t\u01B0\u1EE3ng.`,
